{"tid":414491,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"香港Hip Hop界 diss/beef 回顧","createTime":"2017-09-26T09:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T12:31:50.000Z","uid":48993,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"48322fc6a923f95dbafe3ba86738a234852470ad","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"近排香港hip hop 界有火藥味，大家都應該留意到<br />\n<br />\n首先係bakerie diss track &quot;DLLM&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JuYLF58Cp2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJuYLF58Cp2M&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f67840b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JuYLF58Cp2M</a><br />\n米奇老味跟住加多一腳 &quot;180K&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gZGCrchFi68\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgZGCrchFi68&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=eed4bd7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gZGCrchFi68</a><br />\n茅頭都係指向Wild$tyle/龍寨Trap House<br />\n<br />\n而先前出現過唔少diss tracks 都值得留意吓<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. Cooking Bitchess diss GTB （2017）</strong><br />\n呢個近期少少，唔太算係hip hop界<br />\n<br />\n事源Serrini喺4月左右創立GTB，並推出single &quot;Green Tea Bitches&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/serruria/gtbgreen-tea-bitchesft-nobody-mix?in=serruria/sets/pop-gtb-serena-n-ruby\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fserruria%2Fgtbgreen-tea-bitchesft-nobody-mix%3Fin%3Dserruria%2Fsets%2Fpop-gtb-serena-n-ruby&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6f537033\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/serruria/gtbgreen-tea-bitchesft-nobody-mix?in=serruria/sets/pop-gtb-serena-n-ruby</a><br />\n<br />\n由火炭麗琪領軍嘅Cooking Bitchess（早於喺年頭成立，周不時喺HKCR有直播。）指GTB concept/idea上有嚴重抄襲嗰種&quot;臭閪主義&quot;之嫌，出咗首&quot;綠茶椰菜花&quot; diss GTB<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soundcloud.com/cooking-bitchess/green_tea_broccoli\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soundcloud.com%2Fcooking-bitchess%2Fgreen_tea_broccoli&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0bb72d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soundcloud.com/cooking-bitchess/green_tea_broccoli</a><br />\n<br />\n有趣順帶一提，<br />\nCooking Bitchess成員同Wild$tyle有密切關係。3月時候&quot;火炭麗琪&quot;搵到YoungQueenz featuring，MV入面都有Wild$tyle 旗下嘅Rappers客串。<br />\n另外近期上載嘅 &quot;保持正面&quot; MV都會見到同一班人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/24fFFxVI_g4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F24fFFxVI_g4&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8b0f383d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/24fFFxVI_g4</a><br />\n<br />\nGTB同米奇老味 friend底，米奇老味8月18日埸show除咗Bakerie之外仲揾咗GTB做supporting，而喺&quot;馬克思&quot;MV度都目到成員Serrini同楊彤蹤影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pxmfaJsKibI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpxmfaJsKibI&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=eefac0c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pxmfaJsKibI</a><br />\n<br />\n唔多唔少對後期bakerie diss wild$tyle 有分黨派影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指證，會keep住update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246fd3f3c54f8eb8889a0db9937806e084ef87d6","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"2. Flashkid vs. Heyo （2011）<br />\n<br />\n不得不提呢次經典beef<br />\n<br />\n（唔係好記得flashkid當時出歌原因，有相關資料嘅巴打可以幫手補充吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFlashkid Summary - Murder Heyo 殺heyo<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FQ_2uUkzbyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFQ_2uUkzbyQ&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ddb2f0ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FQ_2uUkzbyQ</a><br />\n個beat底不停重覆（殺Heyo殺Heyo...）有意模仿/戲謔較早前Heyo屌鳩海洋公園嘅&quot;VSOP&quot;入面 （你老母你老母...）<br />\n<br />\nHeyo - 剝牙<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BHxU1AiqG0M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBHxU1AiqG0M&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a30a68b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BHxU1AiqG0M</a><br />\n自從《花華》從良洗底後，好多人都叫Heyo現場唱&quot;剝牙&quot;但都拒絕再唱。<br />\n記得出呢首歌嗰陣，類似佢話未好好溝通就反擊diss，有D唔好意思，最Hip Hop態度係要溝通。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而奈何首歌寫得出奇地絕核<br />\n由YouTube封面 <br />\n到 歌名 <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Murder</span> &rarr; <span style=\"color: gold;\">剝牙</span> (寓意剝你棚牙)<br />\n再到歌詞 <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我嘅威力係一件生化武器</span> &rarr;<span style=\"color: gold;\">wah！你老味 咁都叫做生化武器 嚇到你 真係冇氣 果一渣餸尾</span><br />\n<br />\n甚至用flow用字都係完美KO Flashkid"},{"pid":"6fa76a4ab0fed08eb57f40fab6c6c8d01250a806","tid":414491,"uid":75783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"cooking bitches<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c4d2f274eb9e2a19277cec8bbb00ef4a6d659e","tid":414491,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"LF2"},{"pid":"aa00884f15fef683a9bfbdb325d898699e219de1","tid":414491,"uid":42862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下少爺gang同wildstyle 有咩關係 <br />\n做咩突然埋堆"},{"pid":"1077c0d61cec419d01e43b903c8cb62e840b322c","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下少爺gang同wildstyle 有咩關係 <br />\n做咩突然埋堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYoungQueenz早前喺Facebook都解釋過，SYG同火炭麗琪都唔喺屬於Wild$tyle<br />\n純推廣 &quot;based music&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/020654_5eaf48a42b6d57b2b6afc29c3de32c1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F020654_5eaf48a42b6d57b2b6afc29c3de32c1a.png&h=1659193f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實早前SYG嘅LV 同奶其都參與過Wild$tyle旗下HGLF嘅mixtape，所以都friend咗一排<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC1t7bPXTPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRC1t7bPXTPQ&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7a828394\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC1t7bPXTPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n06. 215 / KLASSICK ft. LV (Prod.by Jazz Logic)<br />\n09. Outro / 奶其 From SYG<br />\n<br />\n但我又反而唔知柒羊幾時入股SYG，淨係知柒羊隊牛子心失咗蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87ff14beb89dd46dfc61dacca1fd906fd4144d8","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>3. Dirty. R diss MC仁（2010）</strong><br />\n<br />\n無可否認MC仁係香港Hip Hop教父<br />\n由N.T. 到LMF到黃禍／北斗再到個人發展「福建音樂」，都不斷將Hip Hop引入香港<br />\n<br />\n而Dirty. R，自稱行Dirty South風格，但而家應該退出咗，連facebook page都刪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早年開辦潮鋪Baby Ghetto（已結業），賣吓Hip Hop潮流飾物<br />\n另外喺2010年亦都以Cansyde名義舉辦過一屆&quot;Ghetto Rap Stars Rap Battle&quot;，Doughboy同Heyo都做過嘉賓。當中Flashkid都參加過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mK8R0Z-Bvvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmK8R0Z-Bvvs&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d618fa4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mK8R0Z-Bvvs</a><br />\n（柒到唔敢睇，慎入）<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，Dirty. R曾經幫Action Waterfall做過廣告歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5VwZCcSxFHI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5VwZCcSxFHI&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0781bb5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5VwZCcSxFHI</a><br />\n<br />\nDirty. R當時不齒MC仁嘅老屎忽姿態，就寫咗呢首歌<br />\n80bars Diss HK HipHop Mother By Dirty.R<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KizEWftzTqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKizEWftzTqg&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d5801d0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KizEWftzTqg</a><br />\n<br />\n首歌好多個位都係直線抽擊MC仁<br />\n<br />\n0:08 片中出現&quot;封建音樂&quot;，戲謔MC仁自家廠牌&quot;福建音樂&quot;， 就好似當年The Game 唔妥50 cent，話佢條crew G-unit係<strong>G-unot</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1:16 <span style=\"color: pink;\">人哋首歌讚頌神 你就偏偏相反</span><br />\n1:23 <span style=\"color: pink;\">你都夠𤓓 喺MV promote你件新貨</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qJEom5IFsAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqJEom5IFsAE&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f975c613\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qJEom5IFsAE</a><br />\n的而且確，MC仁段verse係有質疑&quot;神&quot;嘅成份，MV入面又真係由Tee到外套到頂帽，都係佢廠牌寧死不屈出品。（MC仁嗰期出現親都係咁著）<br />\n<br />\n1:46 <span style=\"color: pink;\">冇貨咪出聲 快D Train up你班𡃁ken</span> <br />\n- 講緊黃禍／北斗<br />\n<br />\n2:18 <span style=\"color: pink;\">十年出一首歌 仲得16個bar</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-cGuxcKfJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2-cGuxcKfJ8&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=95755cbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-cGuxcKfJ8</a><br />\n相信係指呢首，段verse 16個bar，首歌2009年，但其實喺2008年就推出咗solo大碟&quot;福建音樂&quot;<br />\n<br />\n2:56 <span style=\"color: pink;\">我支咪嘅作用就係要嘮嘈 我支咪嘅作用就係要控訴</span><br />\n戲謔 LMF - &quot;WTF&quot; MC&nbsp;仁嘅第一part<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我支咪嘅作用就係要嚟講社會嘅問題我就要嘮嘈我就要控訴</span><br />\n<br />\n3:30 <span style=\"color: pink;\">經典樂隊裡面竟有一人丟架</span><br />\n- 經典樂隊 = LMF<br />\n<br />\n陳強當年都喺903訪問佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S-SadvZRKmc?list=PLC5C8C855CE5DF023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS-SadvZRKmc%3Flist%3DPLC5C8C855CE5DF023&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8bd8faf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S-SadvZRKmc?list=PLC5C8C855CE5DF023</a>"},{"pid":"03d571511d46eb918303e3adcc7166c33afe88ec","tid":414491,"uid":103357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下少爺gang同wildstyle 有咩關係 <br />\n做咩突然埋堆</blockquote><br />\n同埋點解SYG而家係個群組度要追擊個vision？"},{"pid":"cb4d491f83267474c48414d184af0e981947dde3","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下少爺gang同wildstyle 有咩關係 <br />\n做咩突然埋堆</blockquote><br />\n同埋點解SYG而家係個群組度要追擊個vision？</blockquote><br />\n我都未研究清楚原因<br />\n<br />\nVisionz同月喬都係soulsic<br />\n而先前SYG奶其同月喬嘅衝突糾纏咗好耐, 喺facebook你屌我我屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 月喬都出過首&quot;beef burger&quot; diss SYG<br />\n所以阿佛喺&quot;超級火炭麗琪&quot;入面最後一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">究竟奶其同阿月喬兩個人幾時先肯結婚</span>"},{"pid":"c84240ec2edd2b9bb954fe897c81c0ffc1d0b821","tid":414491,"uid":103357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下少爺gang同wildstyle 有咩關係 <br />\n做咩突然埋堆</blockquote><br />\n同埋點解SYG而家係個群組度要追擊個vision？</blockquote><br />\n我都未研究清楚原因<br />\n<br />\nVisionz同月喬都係soulsic<br />\n而先前SYG奶其同月喬嘅衝突糾纏咗好耐, 喺facebook你屌我我屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 月喬都出過首&quot;beef burger&quot; diss SYG<br />\n所以阿佛喺&quot;超級火炭麗琪&quot;入面最後一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">究竟奶其同阿月喬兩個人幾時先肯結婚</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係係soulsic對syg定月喬對奶其 我見soulsic班人除咗月喬之外都冇乜回應咁"},{"pid":"72d7fe9d247b4bb54e34b70b0c7e7687299412df","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:21:43.000Z