8T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26460c46decb749bac7eed2c4f7aed0cb71f4546","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/143640_cbbfd06375711ca604d4824f797b0641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F143640_cbbfd06375711ca604d4824f797b0641.jpg&h=3674eea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c32a88c41c168fab2916a724240258864bf1843","tid":414491,"uid":111718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:00:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d9ef5097c0e5cb39bf7fac7d57094bb73c99ac9d","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>4. Arho Sunny diss Dirty. R（2010）</strong><br />\n<br />\n所謂螳螂捕蟬，黃雀在後。<br />\n你diss人同時後面都有人diss你。<br />\n利申：與MC仁完全無關<br />\n<br />\nArho Sunny大家都應該聽過佢個名，2010-2013左右出咗唔少諷刺時弊嘅歌，但好多都remove晒睇唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (有冇巴打有backup呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n而家全面轉做YouTuber，早排同ashly 嘅紏紛都唔少人討論<br />\n近排都有出吓歌嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PU9nWQ11Jmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPU9nWQ11Jmo&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=416e80df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PU9nWQ11Jmo</a><br />\n<br />\n講返正題，Arho Sunny不齒Dirty. R過份消費Hip Hop文化，全部錢字行頭，所以就出咗呢首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4M1M02LNoHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4M1M02LNoHg&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=25fc94a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4M1M02LNoHg</a><br />\n<br />\n歌名&quot;<span style=\"color: gold;\">驚嘥</span>&quot;就係揶揄Dirty. R嘅<span style=\"color: pink;\">Cansyde</span><br />\nChorus仲係咁講買嘢<br />\n<br />\n0:46 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hello 你好 佢叫Dirty Dirty<br />\n你問佢Hip Hop歷史 佢原全唔知<br />\n最叻就係搵錢 最多好似只係銀紙</span><br />\n<br />\n消費hip hop<br />\n<br />\n1:05<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">佢最叻搞battle 搞到一穫泡</span><br />\n<br />\n上回提到Dirty. R個freestyle battle係點嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2:24<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">睇準時機 佢玩埋MJ</span><br />\n<br />\n發死人財<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VkNv1EIH58M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVkNv1EIH58M&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a36eeb9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VkNv1EIH58M</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">延伸聆聽</span></em></strong><br />\n呢首歌連MV捧紅咗 Ashly<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ZLAdl83w8c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0ZLAdl83w8c&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5e476596\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ZLAdl83w8c</a><br />\n2006年Arho Sunny 已經上過翡翠台節目音樂潮＠giv (嗰時仲係無線互動giv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oHfg2RgKdIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoHfg2RgKdIw&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4ce298be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oHfg2RgKdIw</a><br />\n2011年Flashkid居然上台客串Arho Sunny唱&quot;驚嘥&quot;，但佢自己都有參加Dirty. R個battle㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GwcnG4xv_kk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGwcnG4xv_kk&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=71fff5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GwcnG4xv_kk</a>"},{"pid":"4672d55dfd8696984f947b6811a85f4cf2f609ae","tid":414491,"uid":5426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"正 有曬前文後理 再聽返 係唔同d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持樓主"},{"pid":"f5d57d4a0ff28030772409753d8ef48e87f12dc7","tid":414491,"uid":48473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"Bakerie最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0687941ef58995b387a612c5065cc126377750bd","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E9HrmbNiYcU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE9HrmbNiYcU&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1514aafe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E9HrmbNiYcU</a><br />\n奶其尋晚出咗首新歌，大家品評吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD詞好頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a6b5130d111c930793d61e2a9d333854e07fab","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>5. KZ diss Dirty. R and more（2011）</strong><br />\n<br />\n黃雀在後，但係黃雀唔止一隻。<br />\n<br />\n嗰時Dirty. R曾經用iphone嘅&quot;I am T-Pain&quot; App將把聲auto-tuned而出咗一首歌&quot;iphone瘋&quot; (首歌已經失傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n所以KZ就用autotuned出咗呢首歌，諷刺一下，條片仲要係Arho Sunny幫佢整。<br />\n<br />\n呢首算係KZ收山之作第一章，但首歌事實上唔係淨係針對Dirty. R一個，<br />\nKZ有見嗰一代嘅Rapper歌詞質素每況愈下，太多劣質，甚至已經預知現今呢一代嘅Rappers已經失去咗Hip Hop嘅真正意義。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">kz 2011 start from killa zero mixtape - 鬆化 zone ver</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tgwo0GiR0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-tgwo0GiR0w&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c746bd73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tgwo0GiR0w</a><br />\n<br />\n0:42 <span style=\"color: gold;\">哩一首歌 唔係寫俾你 而係寫俾我 係講我自己點講你是非</span><br />\n第一段verse 第一句開宗明義呢首係Diss Track<br />\n<br />\n1:07 <span style=\"color: gold;\">我拎起紙筆 俾人話我老土 都唔知似乜 而家興用電腦<br />\n</span><br />\n用電腦 狹義係指Auto Tuned，廣義其實就指呢一代歌嘅gimmick往往重要過歌詞嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n1:13 <span style=\"color: gold;\">呢啲舊派 就快 過期 恭喜 賀喜 祝我快啲餓死</span><br />\n歸根到底，KZ覺得自己已經跟唔到時代，準備收山，其實diss緊自己。<br />\n<br />\n1:20<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派台歌 電台冇乜點播 喺卡拉OK 冇人點播 我又可以點啵<br />\n或者啲歌詞 要再白痴啲 又或者咪再堅持 咪再發CD</span><br />\nKZ 出過兩隻CD，分別係&quot;畸詩集&quot;同埋&quot;90年代曲&quot;，而&quot;90年代曲&quot;入面嘅&quot;紅日&quot;的而且確派過台，當然播放次數寥寥無幾，始終嗰時主流媒體仲未完全接受到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JuDNrp89bcE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJuDNrp89bcE&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=06be4865\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JuDNrp89bcE</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">延伸聆聽</span></strong></em><br />\nKZ - 算數啦畸詩兄 feat. E1guan<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0TTsViwVTCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0TTsViwVTCs&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0a4fc018\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0TTsViwVTCs</a><br />\n可能真係好似KZ話齋 <span style=\"color: gold;\">或者啲歌詞 要再白痴啲</span>，同徒弟E1guan出咗隻家傳互曉嘅diulama，跟住就有一系列嘅歐美Hip Hop倒模歌。<br />\n其中&quot;算數啦畸詩兄&quot;倒模咗Dr. Dre &amp; Snoop Dogg嘅&quot;Nuthin' But a G Thang&quot;，再度diss自己。<br />\n<br />\nKZ 最後玩歌 - 桑拿 song<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdvxbVm4WHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdvxbVm4WHY&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a0050b70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdvxbVm4WHY</a><br />\n講明最後玩歌，除咗結束咗倒模歌系列之外，仲結束埋Hip Hop生涯。<br />\n<br />\nDoughboy's《Chinglish》album release day - Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ym5KS3nYXG4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYm5KS3nYXG4&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3181d024\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ym5KS3nYXG4</a><br />\n2017年4月Dough Boy新碟發佈會香港站，KZ都有出席支持，Stanvibes就同佢做咗個有趣訪問。<br />\n3:34開始睇<br />\n「我就冇玩架喇，留返俾你哋新嗰D人啦。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四海魚蛋 手打三寶 係咁Rap廣告 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IJlqeG5vZQE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIJlqeG5vZQE&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3074532d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IJlqeG5vZQE</a><br />\n2012年為咗搵食仲整埋D咁嘅歌......"},{"pid":"e6e58f7808b76d05692dc598ff80c1359b9494ca","tid":414491,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"成班小學雞"},{"pid":"518cacc2fefee7892ad08864d6e7114bcec6ede2","tid":414491,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班小學雞</blockquote><br />\n的確有d 位係幾小學雞，但都有d值得反思下"},{"pid":"c5cee38c663e31dbf3830512cad838f065095d17","tid":414491,"uid":22331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"Kz <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4547174eff6ffbf28c0b0339f78311ae784cd700","tid":414491,"uid":5426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201